Lumpy skin disease, Albania
---------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 8 Jul 2016 from Dr Edi Fero, Chief Veterinary Officer, Department, Ministry of Agriculture, Rural Development and Water Administration, Tirana, Albania

Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 28 Jun 2016
Date of confirmation of the event: 6 Jul 2016
Report date: 8 Jul 2016
